@startuml
title Upload Media / Retrieve Signed URL - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Authorized user" as User
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "files-service" as Files
participant "MediaValidator" as Validator
database "files schema" as DB
collections "MinIO / S3" as S3
participant "owning service\ncustomers/vets/visits/billing" as Owner

User -> Web: Select file
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/files multipart
Gateway -> Files: route with JWT claims
Files -> Validator: type, size, checksum
alt valid file
  Files -> S3: putObject(objectKey)
  Files -> DB: persist FileObject metadata
  Files -> Owner: attach file reference to domain resource
  Owner --> Files: accepted
  Files --> Web: fileId + signed read URL
else invalid type/size
  Files --> Web: ProblemDetail 400
end

User -> Web: Open photo/PDF
Web -> Gateway: GET /api/v1/files/{id}/signed-url
Gateway -> Files: authorize actor
Files -> DB: load FileObject + policy
Files -> S3: presignGet(objectKey, ttl)
Files --> Web: signed URL
Web -> S3: GET object via signed URL
@enduml
